name: Aerodrome Volatile DAI-WETH
description: This token represents a Aerodrome liquidity pool. Holders earn fees from users trading in the pool, and can also deposit the LP to Aerodrome's gauges to earn emissions. This volatile pool contains DAI and WETH.
